item.title: CVE-2023-32635|2024-08-02T15:25:35.706Z -- financial%20services%20agency -- xbrl%20data%20create%20application
item.description: XBRL data create application version 7.0 and earlier improperly restricts XML external entity references (XXE). By processing a specially crafted XBRL file, arbitrary files on the system may be read by an attacker.
